page.title: 10WILDLIFE IN THE NEW FOREST
page.content: When I went to the {NEW FOREST}I had good fun. We saw a spider with an egg sack.{MICHAEL}was on top of an ants hill and the ants were going up his arms and legs . When the egg sack came off the mummy spider it must have taken it somewere to be safe . We went on a bit and we saw a dragonfly and we went to look at it and it looked very nice with black and yellow stripes and there were ants on the way.Our teacher moved a stick and the ants put their{antennae}together and told the other ants aboutthe stick in the path . When we went on a bit more I saw a dragonfly but this one was green all over and then we were coming back to school.
